Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaiba vs the Eighth Duelist"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive that Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for the fourth battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, you need to watch the next Duel for the sake of your next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was having the eye surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your encouragement made\N me feel very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} is battling by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I won't be able to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to be by her side, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I will watch over Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you have to do now is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go back to the heart of the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just one step, you're moving forward, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} would certainly say that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, Honda-{\i1}san{\i0} and Otogi-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and every one of you who has given me courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could take off the bandages of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing about Dueling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can at least do my best to help out my friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, take care of Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ra card Malik owns...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of secrets lie in its text?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, do you understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, big brother.  Although I'm using the computer network of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's taking a while to analyze the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm accessing the host computer of Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?  When you've analyzed it, contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now hold the fourth Duel of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, watch me!\N This will be a battle for the God Cards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the title of 'Duel King'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to settle the score with you,\N I {\i1}will{\i0} win this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Kaiba...\N He's just as arrogant as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels more like he's\N just trying to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me see the skills of a prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This unknown Duelist who hasn't shown themselves yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who cares?! I'll crush any foe who stands before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he finally shows himself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth match! Seto Kaiba VS...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!  You've got {\i1}some{\i0} nerve, making {\i1}me{\i0} wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you don't want to be here, it's fine for you to surrender now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contestant Number 8, your name please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ishizu. Ishizu Ishtar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, isn't that person the one we met at the Egyptian exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am Ishizu Ishtar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My family has kept watch over the king's memories for over 3,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am guided here by my own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain it in a way I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can it be that {\b0}you{\b1} have been chosen too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is my younger little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now being controlled by another personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is only a sorrowful vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save my younger brother, Malik, I will win this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't that scumbag Malik say his last name was Ishtar too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure give off a similar feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, I swear I will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay out of this, weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, this Millennium Tauk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has the power to see into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will {\i1}lose{\i0} your battle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More of that Occult rubbish again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown tired of your ridiculous jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that gave the God Card, the Obelisk at the museum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and asked for my help in destroying the Ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this tournament was held for that sole purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kaiba and this woman secretly planned this tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you say you will {\i1}defeat{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a {\i1}much{\i0} better impression than our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of the Ghouls, thieves who raid Duelists all over the world in secrecy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my younger brother, Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not the Malik over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dear sister,\N is it time to disclose this secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the leader of the Ghouls,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's natural to not forgive him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the crime of stealing Rare Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But compared with this, there's a more terrifying threat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Malik now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's why you spoke to me and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,asked me to hold this tournament as bait for the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep winning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and die with the one dominating Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know what drives your resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but something still bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use me for your goals and then claim you're going to {\i1}beat{\i0} me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what his relationship with you is like,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will crush you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying\Nyou can see the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ishizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your superstitious Occult paraphernalia won't work on {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my {\i1}cards{\i0}\Nto decide my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll use the power of the Obelisk {\i1}you{\i0} handed me to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what if that very same Obelisk instead leads you to a path of destruction...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Declare the start of the Duel, Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the Duel begin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto, I can see everything in your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're summoning\N Blood Vorse in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Blood Vorse in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, you will set one reverse card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is the same as my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she really has the power to see into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see him get his butt kicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then my plan to wipe the floor with Kaiba myself would be ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I don't know what to pick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really {\i1}not{\i0} that tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba won't lose so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against {\i1}Jounouchi{\i0}, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, the power of the Millennium Tauk ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The power of the Millennium Items aren't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to get information from Industrial Illusion's data banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keldo in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she didn't look at the card she drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Ishizu really seen everything that will happen in this match?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean that she already knows what
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,card she will draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai did the same thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same as the Aroma Tactics trick Mai was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is too strong up here, so the fragrance would just blow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This woman's abilities are {\b0}far{\b1} from a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I activate a Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow Traveler of the Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fellow Traveler of the Grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An annoying card that exposes both of our hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll make my discard my best cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such a humiliating card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please discard Kaiser Glider and Fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That woman knew the cards in my hand without seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can it be some kind of trick that lets her see my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see {\i1}your{\i0} cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discard Resurrection of the Dead and Revival Magic from your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How scary. Is my dear elder sister using{\b0} that{\b1} strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the surfaced Malik couldn't beat that deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only {\b0}I{\b1} can defeat that tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...! The evil being that lies within my brother's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will win this Duel and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}bury you in the\N darkness with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your precious little brother has been sealed {\i1}deep{\i0} within my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Vorse, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keldo is eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?\N Is this what you saw in your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you look into the future, you should look at the enemy right in front of you, Ishizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen everything concerning this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cards you will play...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how you will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}you{\i0} who doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think using a {\i1}faint{\i0} would\Nwork with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my next turn, I will use this magic card Shrink
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and lower the Attack Power of Blood Vorse by half as an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll invoke my face-down card, the Virus Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will destroy your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu's power is certainly eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kaiba has Obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if Ishizu-{\i0}san{\i1}'s\N power is the real deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it doesn't matter how\N good Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s deck is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will see the answer soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I will set a reverse card on the field.  My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come, attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the moment your Monster attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can activate the\N Shrink and Virus cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Mudora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before the power of the Millennium Tauk,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even the best Duelists fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll lose your\N Life Points along with Obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is your inescapable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ordinarily, the power to predict the future should never be used in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I can save Malik's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will offer my life to the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as punishment for my sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, on this turn I equip Mudora with the Equipment Card, Sword of Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mudora's Attack Power\N goes up by 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You fell for it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall into the trap of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He shrunk his own Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then infected it with the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that this Dark Attribute Monster has less than 1000 Attack Points, he becomes the carrier of the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Monsters on your field and in your deck are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Kaiba's Deck Destruction Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just killed every powerful Monster in Ishizu's deck with that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you predict this\N strategy as well, Ishizu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put all of your Monsters with 1500 Attack or higher into the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the Virus Combo has left only weak Monsters in Ishizu's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But my Virus Combo isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will invoke this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords of Light!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you plan to strengthen your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use this to escape demise during the next three turns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not planning to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light shall act as a {\i1}countdown{\i0} to your {\i1}defeat{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During these three turns, you will draw the card
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will decide your defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the sleep-talking gibberish for when you're actually {\i1}asleep{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already got one foot in the grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one whose lost their best cards, their main battle force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just wait out these three turns and pray that you draw better cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will set one card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magic Removal Virus Cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll wipe out every Magic Card in your deck on my next round!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishizu, I will pluck every feather from your wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and bring you back to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto Kaiba... You've played right into my elder sister's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now it's simply a question of {\b0}when{\b1} she will play {\b0}that card{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming. My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I put one card in reverse. Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Didn't you draw a {\i1}Monster{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see the future\Nof my failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll draw the card which\Nguides you to destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in just two turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} not the one\N who's putting on a show here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!\Nthe card I'll draw next...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every card I'll draw after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are nothing short of the road you're walking on that will lead to your loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's always saying the same crap,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you think\N he's being a bit impractical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if someone told you they could see your future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how could you {\i1}not{\i0} get frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, big brother!\N You've backed her into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light are useless in front of {\i1}my{\i0} brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one more turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ishizu, this is the supposed "countdown to my loss"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that you played the Sealing Swords of Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet couldn't manage to get a {\i1}single{\i0} card out on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about struggling a bit {\i1}more{\i0} for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what you draw, all that awaits you is a pit of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bomb Held By A Tribute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And wen this turn ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The countdown to your loss has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though you gave yourself three more turns to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you couldn't even play a mere Wall Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you even {\i1}say{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of the Swords of Sealing Light have vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can {\b0}feel{\b1} it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God's pulse being\N emitted from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you aware of the existence of three legendary rare cards Pegasus hid away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are the three Illusionary Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Giant War God Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Osiris the Heaven Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is said the one to acquire these three rare cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will reign over the world of Duels...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and be given the highest ranking Duelist's title...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the title of "King of Kings".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like you to help us get the two remaining God Cards back from the Ghoul Rare Card Hunters that stole them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Giant War God Obelisk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to take back the two cards that were stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am entrusting you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like handing me Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was a huge miscalculated\N {\b0}miss{\b1} on your part!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God is in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Gremlin! Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future is infinite!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past is merely a string of footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff that happened long before my time in the past has nothing to do with {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu, the same goes for the fact that you {\i1}gave{\i0} me a God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But God's hand will\N {\b0}not{\b1} bring you a path of {\b0}victory{\b1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Ishizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be controlled by the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road I walk {\i1}myself{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is what determines my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(128,133)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Virus Combo affecting Ishizu's cards
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with\Nher unusual calmness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Trap Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their decks and\Nthe cards in the gave
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been exchanged!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba uses his six cards
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} Tries hard to call Obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the future be\Nwhat Ishizu predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Attack Changes the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel, Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
